@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((0.50 + 0.02) * ((tmp + 0.12 - v2 + 0.37) - wp.cos(v0 + 0.70)))
    tmp = 0.90
    v1 = wp.sin(((v0 + 0.66 + v1 + 0.96) * wp.abs(tmp + 0.28)))
    tmp = 0.89
    tmp = v1
    v2 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.70 / tmp + 0.54)) / ((v2 + 0.38 / v2 + 0.57) * tmp))
    tmp = ((tmp / wp.sin(v1 + 0.30)) / v1)
    v0 = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.73 * v1 + 0.90)) - (wp.cos(v2 + 0.20) / wp.exp(v0 + 0.90)))
    data[tid] = v0
